    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>with the <strong>mayo</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lemon mayo</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
