    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> spinach</strong> and <strong>blanched peas </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the spinach has wilted – these are your <strong>buttery</strong> <strong>greens</strong></p>",
